      <title>钢铁、铝关税将影响数百万吨进口产品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/steel-aluminum-tariffs-will-impact-millions-of-tons-of-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铝和钢铁是唐纳德·特朗普总统第一任期内首批实施的关税之一。预计周六将恢复这些措施，这将影响数百万吨进口金属。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/steel-aluminum-tariffs-will-impact-millions-of-tons-of-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 22:57:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>两名穆迪评级分析师在华盛顿特区美国空难中丧生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/two-moody-s-ratings-analysts-killed-in-american-air-crash-in-dc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级公司表示，周三晚间，美国航空集团公司一架客机与一架军用直升机在华盛顿空中相撞，造成 67 名乘客和机组人员遇难，其中包括该公司两名分析师克里斯托弗·柯林斯 (Christopher Collins) 和梅利莎·尼坎德里 (Melissa Nicandri)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/two-moody-s-ratings-analysts-killed-in-american-air-crash-in-dc</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 22:42:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通计划在关税担忧中交付价值 40 亿美元的美国黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-plans-4-billion-gold-delivery-in-us-amid-tariff-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司将于 2 月份在纽约根据期货合约交付价值超过 40 亿美元的金条，而此时正值金价飙升和进口关税威胁引发全球范围内将黄金运往美国的浪潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-plans-4-billion-gold-delivery-in-us-amid-tariff-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 18:12:26 GMT</pubDate>
